---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Education" description="Educational resources about hoarding disorder for individuals, families, and communities.">

  <div class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Education</h1>
      <h2>Building Understanding and Awareness</h2>

      <p>At the Minnesota Hoarding Task Force, we believe that education is the foundation for fostering understanding, compassion, and action. Our educational resources are designed to inform individuals, families, and communities about hoarding disorder, its challenges, and the steps needed to address it.</p>

      <p>Through workshops, community presentations, and a library of resources, we empower people to recognize the signs of hoarding, understand its impact, and connect with the support systems available. Whether you're seeking guidance for a loved one, training as a professional, or learning to better support your community, our mission is to provide accessible, practical knowledge that drives meaningful change.</p>

      <div class="videos-grid">
        <div class="video-embed">
          <iframe
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/I13Q37paLzA"
            title="MNHTF 2024 - Supporting Loved Ones with Anxiety - Guest Speaker Jayme Kolbo, LPCC"
            width="560"
            height="315"
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
            allowfullscreen
            loading="lazy"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
        <div class="video-embed">
          <iframe
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Z1LZY1l6dNY"
            title="MNHTF hosts Bridging.org"
            width="560"
            height="315"
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
            allowfullscreen
            loading="lazy"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
        <div class="video-embed">
          <iframe
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/iy7kcA3GC1Q"
            title="MNHTF Guest Speaker Dakota County August 1, 2024"
            width="560"
            height="315"
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
            allowfullscreen
            loading="lazy"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="youtube-cta">
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@mnhoardingtaskforce1757" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">MNHTF YouTube Channel</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
.videos-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-6);
  margin: var(--space-8) 0;
}
.video-embed {
  position: relative;
  padding-bottom: 56.25%;
  height: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
  border-radius: 8px;
}
.video-embed iframe {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
}
.youtube-cta {
  margin-top: var(--space-8);
  text-align: center;
}
</style>
